HEADWORD: Xylotomy
<hw>Xy*lot"o*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>xylo-</ets> + <ets>-tomy</ets>.]</ety> <def>Art of preparing
